This project performs the following data preprocessing steps:

- Import required libraries
- Load the Titanic dataset
- Display the **Age** column
- Handle missing values
- Encode categorical data
- Convert data types
- Scale numerical features
- Select features and target
- Split the dataset into training and testing sets
- Save the cleaned dataset
- Display the saved file location

These preprocessing steps prepare the dataset for building accurate and reliable Machine Learning models.







